avnos B.C.|Keravnos]] | style="font-size:90%;" |'''[[2017–18 FIBA Europe Cup|2017–18]]''' |- | rowspan="3"|{{flagicon|SVK}} [[Slovak Extraliga (basketball)|Slovakia]] (3) | <center> 1</center> || [[MBK Komárno|Komárno]] | style="font-size:90%;" |[[2015–16 FIBA Europe Cup|2015–16]] |- | <center> 1</center> || [[BK Inter Bratislava|Inter Bratislava]] | style="font-size:90%;" |[[2015–16 FIBA Europe Cup|2015–16]] |- | <center> 1</center> || [[BC Prievidza|Prievidza]] | style="font-size:90%;" |[[2016–17 FIBA Europe Cup|2016–17]] |- | rowspan="3"|{{flagicon|AUT}} [[Österreichische Basketball Bundesliga|Austria]] (3) | <center> 2</center> || [[Kapfenberg Bulls]] | style="font-size:90%;" |[[2015–16 FIBA Europe Cup|2015–16]], [[2017–18 FIBA Europe Cup|2017–18]] |- | <center> 1</center> || [[Güssing Knights]] | style="font-size:90%;" |[[2015–16 FIBA Europe Cup|2015–16]] |- | <center> 1</center> || [[Oberwart Gunners]] | style="font-size:90%;" |[[2016–17 FIBA Europe Cup|2016–17]] |- | rowspan="3"|{{flagicon|NED}} [[Dutch Basketball League|Netherlands]] (3) | <center> 3</center> || [[Donar Groningen|Donar]] | style="font-size:90%;" |[[2015–16 FIBA Europe Cup|2015–16]], [[2016–17 FIBA Europe Cup|2016–17]], '''[[2017–18 FIBA Europe Cup|2017–18]]''' |- | <center> 1</center> || [[Den Bosch Basketball|Den Bosch]] | style="font-size:90%;" |[[2015–16 FIBA Europe Cup|2015–16]] |- | <center> 1</center> || [[BS Leiden|Leiden]] | style="font-size:90%;" |[[2015–16 FIBA Europe Cup|2015–16]] |- | rowspan="2"|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Korisliiga|Finland]] (2) | <center> 2</center> || [[Kataja Basket|Kataja]] | style="font-size:90%;" | [[2015–16 FIBA Europe Cup|2015–16]], [[2017–18 FIBA Europe Cup|2017–18]] |- | <center> 1</center> || [[KTP-Basket|KTP]] | style="font-size:90%;" |[[2015–16 FIBA Europe Cup|2015–16]] |- | rowspan="3"|{{flagicon|ISR}} [[Israeli Basketball Super League|Israel]] (3) | <center> 2</center> || [[Bnei Herzliya]] | style="font-size:90%;" | [[2016–17 FIBA Europe Cup|2016–17]], [