'''Samuel Baláž''' (born 25 August 1999) is a Slovak [[Canoe sprint|sprint canoeist]].

He participated at the [[2018 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships]].<ref>[https://timetable.canoesprintportugal.com/uploads/XML_Provas/39/pdf/157.pdf K-4 1000 m results]</ref>

